### Health check
GET http://localhost:8000/health

### List providers
GET http://localhost:8000/providers

### Get all pricing data
GET http://localhost:8000/pricing

### Filter by provider
GET http://localhost:8000/pricing?source=Notion

### Filter by plan
GET http://localhost:8000/pricing?plan=Business

### Get price anomalies (ML)
GET http://localhost:8000/anomalies
